high_descs: Move forward to the sink, turn left, walk until the stove is on your right, then turn right.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left, walk forward one step, then turn right to face the garbage can.
Cut the apple into three pieces.
Turn right, walk forward one step, then turn left to face the counter.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn left, walk forward one step, and turn right to face the garbage can.
Pick up the piece of apple that's closest to you.
Turn around, walk to the counter, then turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the apple in the sink, rinse it, then remove it.
Turn around, walk to the wall, then turn left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the apple piece inside.
anns.task_desc: Clean and wash an apple piece, then microwave it.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter that is left of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left, move to the bin at the end of the counter.
Slice the apple in the bin.
Turn right, move to the counter that is left of the stove.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn left, move to the bin at the end of the counter.
Pick up a section of apple from the bin.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the apple section in the stove, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the microwave.
Place the apple section in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a section of apple into the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the counter left of the stove
Pick up the knife on the counter
Go to the bin
Cut the apple in the bin
Go to the counter
Place the knife on the counter
Go to the bin
Pick up an apple piece from the bin
Go to the sink
Wash the apple piece in the sink
Go to the microwave
Place the apple piece in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Place a washed apple piece in a microwave
